152
00:10:16,574 --> 00:10:19,134
Vamos, tenemos que irnos.

153
00:10:19,177 --> 00:10:20,166
Bienvenida a casa.

154
00:10:44,368 --> 00:10:46,199
Bien, Marla.

155
00:10:47,171 --> 00:10:49,230
